新京报旗下摄影类公众号。
Photographic Public Number of the Beijing News.
新京报两路记者分别前往北京海淀区和丰台区集中医学观察点，探访其日常运行情况。
Two reporters from the Beijing News traveled to Haidian District and Fengtai District in Beijing to gather medical observation points and visit their daily operation.
全文2312字，阅读约需4.5分钟曾与新冠肺炎确诊病例或疑似病例密切接触，但尚无发热、咳嗽等明显发病症状，且不具备条件在家或医院隔离的人员，应该去哪里隔离？从外地，特别是武汉返京，需要进行14天隔离观察但不具备居家隔离条件的人员，应该去哪里隔离？2月21日，新京报两路记者分别前往北京海淀区和丰台区集中医学观察点，探访其日常运行情况。
It takes about 4.5 minutes to read the full text of 2312 words and read it in close contact with the confirmed or suspected cases of Newly Coronary Pneumonia, but have no obvious symptoms such as fever and cough, and are not equipped for isolation at home or in hospital.
▲海淀区集中医学观察点，11时，120急救车送来一名“客人”（新冠肺炎密切接触者）。
Haidian District Centralized Medical Observation Point, at 11: 00, 120 ambulance brought a "guest" (close contacts with the New Crown Pneumonia).
新京报记者 浦峰 摄据海淀区集中医学观察点工作人员介绍，排查发现密切接触者后，经本人同意，会将其由120转运车送到中心进行14天的集中医学观察。
According to the staff of Haidian District Centralized Medical Observation Center, the staff of the Beijing News Pu Feng will be transported by 120 transporter to the center for 14 days of intensive medical observation after close contact is found.
此外，还会为病毒检测阳性但未达到医院收治标准的人员设置专区隔离观察。
In addition, special area isolation observation will be set up for persons who are positive for the virus but do not meet hospital admission criteria.
海淀区集中医学观察点坐落在凤凰岭山脚下，由一家拥有独立院落的酒店改造而成。
Located at the foot of Phoenix Hills, Haidian District Centralized Medical Observation Point is converted from a hotel with a separate compound.
中心于1月29日启用，可接收110人。
The centre opened on 29 January and can accommodate 110 persons.
除酒店原有62名工作人员外，中心还派驻了包括区卫健委、疾控、公安等多个部门的40余人工作专班。
In addition to the original 62 staff of the hotel, the center also has more than 40 full-time work classes, including district health committees, disease control, public security and other departments.
▲海淀区集中医学观察点，工作人员为新来的“客人”准备电卡。
Haidian District concentrated medical observation points, the staff for the new "guests" to prepare electric cards.
新京报记者浦峰 摄为缓解被观察者的紧张情绪，工作人员将他们统一称为“客人”。
Beijing News reporter Pufeng to ease the tension of the observers, staff call them "guests."
客房内空调、电视、wifi等设施一应俱全，生活用品等需求由工作组协调解决。
Room air conditioning, TV, Wifi and other facilities are available, such as daily necessities coordinated by the working group.
“除了不能出门，跟住酒店没多大差别。
"It's not very different from staying in a hotel except that you can't go out.
”一位入住者告诉记者。
One resident told reporters.
▲海淀区集中医学观察点，一名入住“客人”想要将私人钥匙交给隔离点外的家属，工作人员取来钥匙进行消毒后再转交。
At Haidian District Centralized Medical Observation Point, a resident "guest" wanted to hand over his personal key to a family member outside the quarantine point, who took the key to disinfect it before handing it over.
新京报记者浦峰 摄医护人员每天会通过电话对所有“客人”进行体温、症状监测， 24小时值守，发现异常将及时报告。
Peking News reporter Pu Feng medical staff will be called every day to all "guests" temperature, symptom monitoring, 24-hour duty, abnormal will be reported in time.
同时也密切关注他们的心理健康，适时提供心理疏导。
At the same time pay close attention to their mental health and provide timely psychological counseling.
▲海淀区集中医学观察点，“客人”的一日三餐由专人送餐上门，针对“客人”饮食上的特殊要求，观察中心特意准备了合适的饭菜。
Haidian District Centralized Medical Observation Point, "guests" three meals a day from a special person to deliver meals, "guests" on the special requirements, the observation center deliberately prepared appropriate meals.
新京报记者浦峰 摄▲海淀区集中医学观察点，11时50分，工作人员把“客人”的午餐放到大楼门口，再由楼内服务人员送给“客人”，全程无接触配送。
At 11: 50 a.m., the staff put the "guests" lunch at the gate of the building, and the attendants there gave it to the guests, who delivered it without contact.
新京报记者浦峰 摄▲海淀区集中医学观察点，12时4分，工作人员把午餐放到每个门口的凳子上。
At 12: 04 p.m., staff members put lunch on stools at each entrance to the Haidian District, where a reporter from the Beijing News, Pu Feng, keeps medical observation points.
新京报记者浦峰 摄▲海淀区集中医学观察点，放好餐之后，工作人员挨个敲门告知“客人”用餐。
Beijing News reporter Pu Feng area concentrated medical observation point, after the meal, staff knocked on the door to tell "guests" to eat.
新京报记者浦峰 摄隔离区每天三次对全楼公共区域消毒，工作人员会指导“客人”每天对客房擦拭消毒。
Peking News reporter Pu Feng area of separation to disinfect the building three times a day, the staff will guide "guests" to clean and disinfect the rooms every day.
所有生活垃圾均按医疗垃圾处理。
All domestic refuse is treated as medical waste.
▲海淀区集中医学观察点，“客人”用完的餐盒，先装小袋，再装大袋，最后装箱。
Haidian District Centralized Medical Observation Point, "guests" used up the lunch box, first pack small bags, then large bags, and finally box.
新京报记者浦峰 摄▲海淀区集中医学观察点，每个装垃圾的塑料袋和箱子上都标注日期。
The Beijing News reporter Pu Feng has concentrated medical observation points in Haidian District, where the date is marked on every plastic bag and box containing garbage.
新京报记者浦峰 摄▲海淀区集中医学观察点，14时30分，服务组准备用紫外线灯对房间进行消毒。
At 1430 hours, the service team prepared to disinfect the room with ultraviolet light.
新京报记者浦峰 摄与海淀区集中医学观察点类似，位于杜家坎附近，1月28日启用的丰台区集中医学观察点由一家快捷酒店改造而来，接收不具备居家隔离条件的返京人员。
The Peking News reporter Pu Feng She, similar to a medical observation center in Haidian District, is located near Dujiakan. The Centralized Medical Observatory of Fengtai District, opened on January 28, has been converted from a fast-track hotel to accommodate returning residents who do not have the means to live in isolation.
这里目前有55名留观人员，分布在一、二、三层。
There are currently 55 visitors in the first, second and third floors.
▲丰台区集中医学观察点，每一层走廊两侧都对称分布着10余间房，房门紧闭，门外摆着一张矮凳，一旁垃圾桶里的黄色垃圾袋提醒，这里有涉疫垃圾，将按医疗垃圾处理。
Fengtai District concentrated medical observation points, each floor of the corridor on both sides of a symmetrical distribution of more than 10 rooms, the door closed, a low stool outside, a garbage bin in the side of the yellow garbage bag warned that there is plague-related garbage, will be treated as medical waste.
新京报记者浦峰 摄▲丰台区集中医学观察点，陈漫怡护士通过对讲机汇报每个房间需要补充的物品。
Beijing News reporter Pu Fengtai area concentrated medical observation points, nurses Chen Diyi through the walkie-talkie to report each room needs to be replenished.
新京报记者 王飞摄▲丰台区集中医学观察点，陈漫怡护士在为从雷神山医院建设返京的工人测量体温。
Nurse Chan Yun-yee takes temperature for workers returning to Beijing from Lei Shenshan Hospital at a medical observation point in Fengtai District.
新京报记者 王飞摄▲丰台区集中医学观察点，潘恒医生让留观者加强锻炼，教她进行拉伸练习。
Beijing News reporter Wang FeiShe Fengtai District concentrated medical observation point, Dr. Panheng asked the viewer to strengthen the exercise, teach her stretching exercises.
新京报记者 王飞摄▲丰台区集中医学观察点，工作人员每天会对隔离区定时消毒、分发三餐、负责帮留观人员接收快递。
Beijing News reporter Wang Feifei District concentrated medical observation point, staff will regularly disinfect the area of separation, distribution of three meals, responsible for watching people receive express delivery.
新京报记者 王飞摄▲丰台区集中医学观察点，每一名医学观察人员的饭菜和经过消毒的快递，统一放在房间门口，工作人员敲门后离开，医学观察人员自行领取。
Beijing News reporter Wang Feifei District concentrated medical observation points, each medical observer's meals and sterilized express, on the door of the room, staff knocked at the door and left, medical observers to collect their own.
新京报记者 王飞摄▲丰台区集中医学观察点，值班医生逐个给医学观察者打电话，询问当日体温情况。
Beijing News reporter Wang FeiShe Fengtai District concentrated medical observation point, the doctor on duty to the medical observers one by one to inquire about the temperature of the day.
新京报记者 王飞摄刘长富原本是这家快捷酒店的员工，酒店被征用后，刘长富当起了临时的清洁工，每天早晚2次对污水进行消毒处理。
Beijing News reporter Wang Feifei Liu Changfu was originally the staff of this fast-track hotel, the hotel was requisitioned, Liu Changfu as a temporary cleaning workers, morning and night twice a day to disinfect sewage treatment.
▲丰台区集中医学观察点，工作人员每天会定点对污水池进行消毒。
Fengtai District concentrated medical observation points, staff will be fixed daily to sterilize the cesspool.
摄影/新京报记者王飞除了污水消毒，医护人员还要每天对污染区的走廊多次消毒，“只要有人进来过就一定要消毒”。
Photography / Beijing News reporter Wang Fei in addition to sewage disinfection, medical staff have to decontaminate the corridors of the contaminated areas many times a day, "as long as someone comes in, must disinfect."
喷雾式消毒设备体积不小，护士刘曼妮背起来几乎占据了她整个后背，里面是体积为8L的84消毒液，加上设备本身的重量，护士们要在负重20斤的情况下，对走廊进行半小时左右的消毒。
The sprayed equipment was so bulky that nurse Liu Mani carried it almost to the back of her back. It contained 8L of disinfectant 84 and, given the weight of the equipment itself, the nurses had to disinfect the hallway for about half an hour.
▲丰台区集中医学观察点，消毒人员对走廊和垃圾袋进行全方位消毒。
Fengtai District concentrated medical observation points, disinfectors on the corridors and garbage bags to carry out all-round disinfection.
新京报记者 王飞摄▲丰台区集中医学观察点，工作人员对每天送来的快递消毒。
Beijing News reporter Wang Feifei Fengtai District concentrated medical observation points, staff on the daily delivery of express disinfection.
新京报记者 王飞摄房间门外的垃圾桶里是医疗垃圾专用的黄色垃圾袋，涉疫情生活垃圾将统一按照医疗垃圾处理。
The garbage bin outside Wang Fei She's room of the Beijing News is a special yellow garbage bag for medical waste.
宋海军原是王佐镇卫生中心的垃圾清运工，临时过来支援这里的涉疫垃圾收集处理。
The Song Navy was originally a garbage collector at the Wang Zozhen Health Center, temporarily came here to support the garbage collection and treatment of the epidemic.
宋海军每天收集暂存的涉疫垃圾超过90袋。
The Song Navy collected more than 90 bags of temporary plague garbage each day.
▲丰台区集中医学观察点，保洁人员将消毒后的垃圾再次用医用垃圾袋包装后，通过专用通道运出集中医学观察点，打包后由专业运输公司回收处理，每1-2天会来集中清运一次。
Fengtai District concentrated medical observation point, cleaning staff will disinfect the garbage again in medical garbage bags, through a dedicated route out of the central medical observation point, packaging and recycling by professional transport companies, every 1-2 days will come to a centralized cleaning.
新京报记者 王飞摄▲丰台区集中医学观察点，雷神山医院施工单位前来探望医学观察的工人。
Beijing News reporter Wang Feifei District concentrated medical observation points, Lei Shenshan Hospital construction units to visit medical observation workers.
新京报记者 王飞摄▲丰台区集中医学观察点，一名医学观察对象拿着解除医学观察通知单离开观察点。
A medical observer left the observation point with a medical notice for medical observation in Fengtai District, a reporter for the Beijing News.
新京报记者 王飞摄摄影 新京报记者 浦峰 王飞文字 新京报记者 周依 姜慧梓编辑 陈婉婷 校对 付春愔点击下图进入"全国新型冠状病毒感染肺炎实时地图"值班编辑 花木南吾彦祖新冠病毒命名含有SARS，高福、石正丽发文反对女性医护人员剃光头出征：被赞美的逆行者，被忽略的女性中疾控7万多新冠病例分析：八成轻中症，病死率男比女高本文部分内容首发自新京报公号“拍者”未经新京报书面授权不得转载使用欢迎朋友圈分享。
